      "type": "html",
      "text": "\nA [[Wiki Page]] may have as its purpose to support a conversation. Such a page can be refactored by moving consensus items to the top or to another page. This is risky, unless there really is consensus. Therefore refactor consensus only if you are sure there is some.",
      "id": "d8cb24572489be90c206d6e158e0f638"
